* [[浅田棘带吸虫|浅田棘带吸虫]] ''Centrocestus asadai'' Mishima, 1959
* ''Centrocestus caninus'' Leiper, 1913
* ''Centrocestus cuspidatus'' (Looss, 1896) Looss, 1899
* [[美丽棘带吸虫|美丽棘带吸虫]] ''Centrocestus formosanus'' (Nishigori, 1924) Price, 1932
* ''Centrocestus fossilisi'' Singh, Kumar, Arya & Anjum, 2005
* ''Centrocestus polyspinosus'' Kobayashi, 1942
* [[台湾棘带吸虫|台湾棘带吸虫]] ''Centrocestus taiwanense''
* ''Centrocestus unequiorchalis'' Saad, 1997
